data.title: Aerosis - Zen Hyperbabble
data.description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

Over 120 minutes of high-quality Goa trance and psytrance music from all over the world is presented on Dimensional Gateway sequel. The style of the first part can be described as darker and more experimental while the second part focuses more on melodic side of Goa trance. Download Dimensional Gateway 2 - http://www.neogoa.net/dimensional-gateway-2

Tracklist:

Part 1 
01 - PharaOm & Leyra - Intro(spection) (137 BPM)
